{
  "description": "A wide-angle view of a waterfront cityscape under a bright blue sky. The scene features a dense collection of buildings of varying heights and architectural styles nestled on a hillside overlooking a body of water. Prominently visible in the background is the iconic red Golden Gate Bridge. In the foreground, there's a long, low-lying structure with numerous arched windows and doorways, likely a warehouse or industrial building, extending along the waterfront. The buildings on the hillside are primarily residential, with a mix of apartments and houses. The color palette is dominated by blues of the water and sky, the red of the bridge, and the muted tones of the buildings, ranging from beige and white to gray and brown. The overall scene conveys a sense of urban density and coastal beauty.",
